---
source: crates/test-framework/src/snapshot/mod.rs
description: "Query: clickbench_q32"
---
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |   Federated                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |  Limit: skip=0, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |   Sort: c DESC NULLS FIRST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |     Projection: hits.WatchID, hits.ClientIP, count(Int64(1)) AS c, sum(hits.IsRefresh), avg(hits.ResolutionWidth)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |       Aggregate: groupBy=[[hits.WatchID, hits.ClientIP]], aggr=[[count(Int64(1)), sum(hits.IsRefresh), avg(hits.ResolutionWidth)]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |         Filter: CAST(hits.SearchPhrase AS Utf8View) != Utf8("")                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |           TableScan: hits projection=[WatchID, ClientIP, IsRefresh, ResolutionWidth, SearchPhrase]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
| physical_plan | BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |   SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |     CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |       VirtualExecutionPlan name=duckdb compute_context=:memory: initial_sql=SELECT "hits"."WatchID", "hits"."ClientIP", count(1) AS "c", sum("hits"."IsRefresh"), avg("hits"."ResolutionWidth") FROM "hits" WHERE (CAST("hits"."SearchPhrase" AS VARCHAR) <> '') GROUP BY "hits"."WatchID", "hits"."ClientIP" ORDER BY "c" DESC NULLS FIRST LIMIT 10 |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
